public interface JanusGraphSchemaElement
extends Namifiable
Marks any element that is part of a JanusGraph Schema. JanusGraph Schema elements can be uniquely identified by their name.

A JanusGraph Schema element is either a JanusGraphSchemaType or an index definition, i.e. JanusGraphIndex or RelationTypeIndex.

作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
